tutorial_talks.content: There are Record Realms that exist deep within the paintings you've already restored, kupo.
tutorial_talks.speaker: moogle

tutorial_talks.content: My research has revealed that by restoring these deep records, we can make all the records stronger, kupo!
tutorial_talks.speaker: moogle

tutorial_talks.content: These are the "Elite" Record Realms, kupo. Master a Classic Dungeon to access its elite counterpart!
tutorial_talks.speaker: moogle

tutorial_talks.content: But it's worth it, kupo! Completing these Elite Dungeons may be the only way to keep the records safe!
tutorial_talks.speaker: moogle

tutorial_talks.content: Just expect to meet a bit more resistance in the Elite Dungeons. The foes you'll face are a LOT tougher, kupo!
tutorial_talks.speaker: moogle

tutorial_talks.content: Maybe a little tough for you right now, {DESI}...but soon!
tutorial_talks.speaker: moogle
